This is how to poly of xs and x:
  Remember that total is 0
  Remember that power is 1
  Do this xs's length times:
    Remember that i is diff of xs's length and power
    Remember that coeff is item i in xs
    Remember that total is sum of total and (product of coeff and power)
    Remember that power is product of power and x
  End do
  The answer is total
